{"tid":2357284,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"陶傑：國會暴動的深層次理由","createTime":"2021-01-07T10:12:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T13:25:44.000Z","uid":201464,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5a37f934301d0df2f3106e3832edb902052339c8","tid":2357284,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T10:12:49.000Z","msg":"陶傑：在國會內被警察槍殺的女示威者鮑碧德（Ashili Babbitt ) ，來自加州聖地牙哥，從軍14年，品格良好，是川普的堅定支持者。被槍殺時並無攜帶武器。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n比起半年前在明尼蘇達州被槍殺的黑人「佛洛伊德」，鮑碧德之死，由 All Lives Matter 的平等角度，一樣的慘烈。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n但由於白左只容許Black Lives Matter, 只有BLM才是神聖的；若變成ALM，就是納粹主義。因此沒有女權主義者為她喊冤，沒有人權組織為她的死在幾十個城市展開暴動。在邏輯上，這位和平的白人女性抗議者之死，她支持川普，只是一名「極右份子」被「公義」鎮壓。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n由這一點切入，或許會明白國會暴動的深層次理由。<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBLM 和反法西斯極左組織在選舉期間街頭暴動，川普的支持者在選舉後的國會也暴動。牛頓物理學定律：這個世界上，有作用力，必有反作用力。成王敗寇，不但歷史由勝利者寫，黑白是非也由「勝利者」決定，取得勝利亦即奪取權力的過程，是否光明正大，是另一回事。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n此所以政治之複雜和險惡，需要非常清醒的獨立頭腦，在一個紛亂的世界，面對任何危機，都要用邏輯常識一思再三想想。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tokit.channel/posts/4839929566079528\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftokit.channel%2Fposts%2F4839929566079528&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z1NDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=2de4e079\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/tokit.channel/posts/4839929566079528</a>"},{"pid":"cfb5477493947d95b98b00c2a345859ae55c895f","tid":2357284,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T10:15:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18e2850b7a8633076af8ff58280cc809981d12fb","tid":2357284,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T10:17:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ac2c3bd05fd25cf1caf0a5dcbf39fda06f9d3a8","tid":2357284,"uid":194120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T10:20:07.000Z","msg":"今次開鎗傳聞係特工同警察又唔同,特工做嘢比起警察隨時係格殺勿論."},{"pid":"21ff02c0e2681f01deb569f29c4f64bfe31a4cc2","tid":2357284,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T10:20:50.000Z","msg":"<em></em>"},{"pid":"37bc255bc552803b7cd9b3c92420f9e51ec56099","tid":2357284,"uid":60924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T10:25:20.000Z","msg":"今晚才子繼續光明頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45e23e0a40a0dfcfa0e66e279007b7d7c641222d","tid":2357284,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T13:25:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"861e34354ab9a750f385050a55045d08a2b875bf","tid":2357284,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T13:25:44.000Z","msg":"引戰波台友: 陶傑係左膠"}]}